verbose_text: Finally, co-treatment with SB225002 antagonized functional enhancements in KM CFU numbers mediated by 1,25 (OH) D3 or calcipotriol during in vitro methylcellulose culture (XREF_FIG) (con versus 1,25 (OH) D3, p < 0.01; con versus calcipotriol, p < 0.01; con versus SB225002, p < 0.05; con versus 1,25 (OH) D3 + SB25502, N.S.; con versus calcipotriol + SB25502, N.S.
